Description: Modern FTP/SFTP client with PyQt6 GUI
 AuroraFTP is a modern, secure, and user-friendly FTP/SFTP client for Linux
 built with Python and PyQt6. It provides a clean dual-pane interface for
 managing file transfers between local and remote systems.
 .
 Key features include:
  * Support for FTP, FTPS, and SFTP protocols
  * Secure credential storage using system keyring
  * Drag-and-drop file operations
  * Multi-threaded transfer queue with progress tracking
  * Site manager for connection profiles
  * Folder synchronization capabilities
  * Real-time transfer monitoring and logging
 .
 AuroraFTP emphasizes security by using encrypted credential storage,
 SSH host key verification, and TLS/SSL support for secure file transfers.
